# AI Impact Assessment (AIA) — Template

!!! info "Tujuan"
    Menilai dampak, risiko, dan kontrol tata kelola AI sebelum/pada saat/pasca implementasi.

## 1. Ringkasan Use Case
- Nama sistem/model:
- Tujuan bisnis & KPI:
- Pemilik proses / penanggung jawab:
- Kategori data (PII/non-PII), sumber data, wilayah:
- Kategori risiko (operasional, kepatuhan, etis, keamanan):

## 2. Konteks & Lingkup
- Domain (banking/fintech/health/IT, dll)
- Sistem terkait (upstream/downstream)
- Boundary (on-prem / cloud; region data residency)

## 3. Klasifikasi Risiko & Dampak
| Aspek | Deskripsi | Level (Low/Med/High) | Catatan |
|---|---|---:|---|
| Privacy/PII |  |  |  |
| Bias & fairness |  |  |  |
| Keamanan model & data |  |  |  |
| Keandalan/robustness |  |  |  |
| Kepatuhan (UU PDP, POJK, Stranas AI) |  |  |  |
| Dampak bisnis & reputasi |  |  |  |

## 4. Data Governance (D dari DPPT)
- Sumber data & legal basis (consent/contract/legitimate interest)
- Data lineage, kualitas, retensi, minimization
- Prosedur anonimisasi/pseudonimisasi (jika ada)

## 5. Process (P dari DPPT)
- Alur proses (from ideation → deployment → monitoring)
- SOC2/ISO/COBIT control yang relevan
- Keterlibatan three lines of defense

## 6. People
- Roles & responsibilities (model owner, data owner, risk, legal, DPO)
- Pelatihan & kompetensi (bias, keamanan, privacy by design)

## 7. Technology
- Arsitektur (on-prem/cloud; komponen; integrasi)
- Keamanan: akses kunci, enkripsi, secret mgmt, audit log
- Observability: logging, tracing, cost/usage guardrails

## 8. Model Governance
- Tipe model (ML tradisional/LLM/RAG/GenAI)
- Dataset & dokumentasi (Datasheet, Model Card)
- Evaluasi (akurasi, fairness, drift, red teaming)
- Rencana retraining/rollback

## 9. Kepatuhan & Regulasi
- **UU PDP**: dasar pemrosesan, hak subjek data, DPA/DPIA
- **POJK** (jika perbankan): manajemen risiko TI, outsourcing/cloud
- **Stranas AI**: prinsip etik, akuntabilitas, transparansi
- **NIST AI RMF**: Map–Measure–Manage–Govern
- **COBIT/TOGAF**: alignment tata kelola & arsitektur

## 10. Crosswalk Kontrol → Evidence → Metrik
| Domain | Kontrol (referensi) | Evidence (bukti siap audit) | Metrik/Kriteria lulus |
|---|---|---|---|
| Data | Data inventory, data minimization (UU PDP, NIST) | Data catalog, DPA, retensi policy | % kolom sensitif termask/hashed |
| Process | Change mgmt, approvals (COBIT/ISO) | RFC, RACI, SoD | SLA persetujuan ≤ X hari |
| People | Pelatihan & akses | Bukti training, matriks akses | % staf selesai training; no orphan access |
| Technology | Security & logging | Konfigurasi IAM, KMS, log audit | 100% akses via IAM; log ≥ 180 hari |
| Model | Eval & bias testing | Laporan evaluasi, model card | Threshold akurasi ≥ X; bias gap ≤ Y |
| Compliance | DPIA/AIA | Form DPIA/AIA, review legal | Status: complete/approved |

